23
00:03:29,360 --> 00:03:30,200
What do you think?

24
00:03:30,560 --> 00:03:31,920
Someone, bring a bowl.

25
00:03:32,440 --> 00:03:33,040
Wait.

26
00:03:35,040 --> 00:03:35,840
There's serious business.

27
00:03:41,400 --> 00:03:43,080
These children in the pictures

28
00:03:43,160 --> 00:03:44,760
