38
00:04:03,360 --> 00:04:04,360
I only know

39
00:04:04,480 --> 00:04:05,800
in Penglai,

40
00:04:06,360 --> 00:04:09,160
if even you can't find the information,

41
00:04:09,440 --> 00:04:11,320
no one can.

42
00:04:12,360 --> 00:04:13,080
Right?

43
00:04:14,560 --> 00:04:15,160
Well,

44
00:04:15,600 --> 00:04:16,840
