Yes.

86
00:06:54,640 --> 00:06:55,840
I do want to see him.

87
00:07:00,120 --> 00:07:01,600
I've been looking for him.

88
00:07:02,120 --> 00:07:02,920
Tell me.

89
00:07:03,640 --> 00:07:05,760
What did you see that night?

90
00:07:10,320 --> 00:07:11,120
I know

