94
00:07:25,160 --> 00:07:26,640
He will come back to life.

95
00:07:34,000 --> 00:07:34,760
Ying'er!

96
00:08:02,080 --> 00:08:04,080
His fatal wound was in the back.

97
00:08:04,880 --> 00:08:06,000
The stab in the chest

98
00:08:06,680 --> 00:08:08,800
was completely different

99
00:08:09,360 --> 00:08:10,600
from the one in the back

100
00:08:10,680 --> 00:08:11,880
in terms of force and angle.

101
00:08:12,360 --> 00:08:13,040
Zhong Fang

102
00:08:13,360 --> 00:08:15,720
