103
00:08:16,600 --> 00:08:17,440
That night,

104
00:08:17,760 --> 00:08:19,800
Zhong Fang's corpse appeared
in the watchtower.

105
00:08:20,400 --> 00:08:21,480
He was not wearing a mask.

106
00:08:22,120 --> 00:08:23,160
It was the first time

107
00:08:23,600 --> 00:08:25,120
Ying'er had seen Zhong Fang's face.

108
00:08:25,560 --> 00:08:26,320
She found

109
00:08:26,720 --> 00:08:28,720
the Rain Master she had been with

110
00:08:29,640 --> 00:08:31,320
was just an ordinary man.

111
00:08:32,080 --> 00:08:33,000
She was in a rage.

112
00:08:34,200 --> 00:08:37,000
She made another stab in his body.

113
00:08:37,840 --> 00:08:38,960
Actually, that knife

114
00:08:39,080 --> 00:08:41,880
was left by the real murderer.

115
00:09:08,560 --> 00:09:09,240
Magistrate Di.

116
00:09:10,400 --> 00:09:11,080
Magistrate Di.

117
00:09:11,680 --> 00:09:12,800
Please save my fellows.

118
00:09:12,800 --> 00:09:13,840
Officer Li wants them dead.

119
00:09:14,320 --> 00:09:15,480
Tell your fellows

120
00:09:16,280 --> 00:09:17,920
to go to see Mr. Hong
in the Magistrate's Office

121
00:09:18,240 --> 00:09:19,520
and tell him to come
to take care of the body.

122
00:09:20,120 --> 00:09:20,640
Go quickly.

123
00:09:20,960 --> 00:09:21,440
Yes.

124
00:09:32,780 --> 00:09:35,520
[Penglai County Magistrate's Office]

125
00:09:35,520 --> 00:09:36,280
Mr. Hong.

126
00:09:37,440 --> 00:09:38,200
Wait a minute.

127
00:09:39,520 --> 00:09:41,440
Miss Cao, how come you are here?

128
00:09:41,560 --> 00:09:42,160
Mr. Hong,

129
00:09:42,440 --> 00:09:43,280
where is Magistrate Di?

130
00:09:43,560 --> 00:09:44,520
Has he come back?

131
00:09:45,800 --> 00:09:47,040
He is still out on a case.

132
00:09:49,760 --> 00:09:50,800
As long as he is fine.

133
00:09:51,720 --> 00:09:52,680
I'll take my leave.

134
00:09:54,040 --> 00:09:54,760
Miss Cao,

135
00:09:56,160 --> 00:09:56,920
Magistrate

136
00:09:57,520 --> 00:09:59,000
will leave Penglai very soon

137
00:09:59,360 --> 00:10:00,280
and go to work in Lanfang County.

138
00:10:01,040 --> 00:10:02,400
He wants to invite you to go with him.

139
00:10:04,120 --> 00:10:06,000
Nobody knows

140
00:10:06,120 --> 00:10:07,600
when he will invite you himself.

141
00:10:07,640 --> 00:10:09,120
So I spoke out of turn.

142
00:10:13,080 --> 00:10:14,440
I have an important case to handle.

143
00:10:14,760 --> 00:10:15,600
I'm leaving.

144
00:10:15,720 --> 00:10:17,240
Miss Cao, take care.

145
00:10:19,120 --> 00:10:19,880
Go.

146
00:10:38,960 --> 00:10:40,040
Why did you do this?

147
00:10:40,400 --> 00:10:41,680
They deserted their posts

148
00:10:41,800 --> 00:10:42,920
and secretly went out of the camp.

149
00:10:42,960 --> 00:10:44,880
This is the punishment they deserve.

150
00:10:45,400 --> 00:10:46,360
I've come here today

151
00:10:46,920 --> 00:10:48,360
to ask you clearly

152
00:10:48,960 --> 00:10:50,600
where they were that night

153
00:10:50,880 --> 00:10:51,640
and why their knives

154
00:10:51,760 --> 00:10:53,440
appeared in the watchtower.

155
00:10:53,680 --> 00:10:55,800
You killed them tonight.

156
00:10:56,040 --> 00:10:57,840
What are you trying to hide?

157
00:10:58,240 --> 00:11:00,440
You mean I was shielding them
from their crimes?

158
00:11:01,040 --> 00:11:03,200
Why did you kill them then?

159
00:11:05,320 --> 00:11:06,440
Answer me!

160
00:11:07,960 --> 00:11:10,240
The dignity of the army is above all.

161
00:11:11,000 --> 00:11:12,000
They made mistakes

162
00:11:12,120 --> 00:11:13,800
and should be punished.

163
00:11:14,200 --> 00:11:16,360
As for how heavy the punishment
should be,

164
00:11:16,880 --> 00:11:18,320
this is my military camp.

165
00:11:18,800 --> 00:11:20,160
I have the final say.

166
00:11:20,880 --> 00:11:22,200
Besides, Magistrate Di,

167
00:11:22,360 --> 00:11:24,280
isn't this the outcome you want?

168
00:11:25,080 --> 00:11:26,960
You suspect them of wrongdoing,

169
00:11:26,960 --> 00:11:28,440
so you came to catch them.

170
00:11:28,760 --> 00:11:30,480
Name them murderers

171
00:11:30,560 --> 00:11:32,240
or even worse

172
00:11:32,520 --> 00:11:34,120
and then sentence them to death.

173
00:11:34,640 --> 00:11:36,400
I solve cases based on evidence.

174
00:11:37,000 --> 00:11:38,520
As long as they didn't do it,

175
00:11:38,520 --> 00:11:39,800
they wouldn't die.

176
00:11:41,200 --> 00:11:42,280
Look at him.

177
00:11:42,800 --> 00:11:44,480
I brought him back from Fang Town.

178
00:11:44,640 --> 00:11:46,000
And him, from Red Valley.

179
00:11:46,120 --> 00:11:47,160
Him, from Liulin.

180
00:11:47,240 --> 00:11:48,480
Him, Qi County.

181
00:11:49,200 --> 00:11:50,360
They had no names.

182
00:11:51,040 --> 00:11:52,280
They were all beggars.

183
00:11:53,120 --> 00:11:54,560
I gave them names.

184
00:11:54,680 --> 00:11:56,160
I taught them the rules.

185
00:11:56,920 --> 00:11:59,120
Their bad habits disappeared
little by little

186
00:11:59,280 --> 00:12:01,160
under my whip.

187
00:12:01,640 --> 00:12:03,120
I've managed to turn them

188
00:12:03,120 --> 00:12:05,480
from scavengers

189
00:12:05,960 --> 00:12:08,280
into dignified soldiers.

190
00:12:08,960 --> 00:12:10,240
Those charges

191
00:12:11,280 --> 00:12:12,000
would've destroyed

192
00:12:12,080 --> 00:12:14,360
their hard-earned

193
00:12:15,080 --> 00:12:16,640
self-esteem.

194
00:12:17,480 --> 00:12:20,080
This matter has not been cleared up yet.

195
00:12:21,840 --> 00:12:25,080
I'd rather they are bodies with dignity.

196
00:12:28,920 --> 00:12:29,760
Magistrate,

197
00:12:30,400 --> 00:12:31,440
leave here

198
00:12:31,480 --> 00:12:32,600
with your men.

199
00:12:37,640 --> 00:12:39,080
This is my military camp.

200
00:12:40,360 --> 00:12:41,320
I have the final say.

201
00:14:23,960 --> 00:14:25,040
It's not a big deal.

202
00:14:25,520 --> 00:14:26,560
Don't be anxious.

203
00:14:26,960 --> 00:14:29,400
I'll get someone to restring it.

204
00:14:29,880 --> 00:14:30,680
No need.

205
00:14:31,400 --> 00:14:32,040
Shall I

206
00:14:32,280 --> 00:14:34,040
invite Magistrate Di to come?

207
00:14:34,920 --> 00:14:35,640
No need.

208
00:14:36,920 --> 00:14:38,040
I don't quite understand.

209
00:14:38,840 --> 00:14:39,720
You are clearly

210
00:14:39,720 --> 00:14:41,200
worried about him.

211
00:14:41,720 --> 00:14:44,360
You know his heart from someone else.

212
00:14:44,800 --> 00:14:46,440
Why are you unwilling to see him?

213
00:14:47,800 --> 00:14:49,720
Recklessly following someone

214
00:14:50,840 --> 00:14:52,600
to a strange place

215
00:14:53,560 --> 00:14:55,080
and unfamiliar surroundings

216
00:14:56,640 --> 00:14:58,200
does not necessarily
lead to a good ending.

217
00:14:59,600 --> 00:15:00,960
That's not necessarily true.

218
00:15:02,120 --> 00:15:03,000
Life is

219
00:15:03,720 --> 00:15:05,120
unpredictable.

220
00:15:06,760 --> 00:15:08,120
You may encounter

221
00:15:08,440 --> 00:15:09,760
anything.

222
00:15:11,120 --> 00:15:13,200
Maybe every disaster
you've ever experienced

223
00:15:16,040 --> 00:15:18,120
can teach you something.

224
00:15:20,200 --> 00:15:21,080
You are either sad

225
00:15:22,080 --> 00:15:23,280
or joyful.

226
00:15:25,680 --> 00:15:26,720
A distant place

227
00:15:27,760 --> 00:15:29,120
actually has nothing.

228
00:15:30,520 --> 00:15:31,560
A distant place

229
00:15:32,240 --> 00:15:34,320
may not necessarily have nothing.

230
00:15:35,160 --> 00:15:35,920
Magistrate

231
00:15:36,480 --> 00:15:38,240
will leave Penglai very soon

232
00:15:38,480 --> 00:15:39,600
and go to work in Lanfang County.

233
00:15:40,160 --> 00:15:41,480
He wants to invite you to go with him.

234
00:15:42,440 --> 00:15:44,400
Nobody knows

235
00:15:44,400 --> 00:15:45,880
when he will invite you himself.

236
00:15:47,000 --> 00:15:48,600
Do you know it will take a tree

237
00:15:49,000 --> 00:15:49,960
at least three to four years

238
00:15:49,960 --> 00:15:51,400
to bear fruits?

239
00:15:52,200 --> 00:15:54,240
But it will bear fruits in the end, right?

240
00:16:14,960 --> 00:16:15,920
I'm here.

241
00:16:18,720 --> 00:16:20,040
I didn't break my word.

242
00:16:21,040 --> 00:16:22,040
I'm back.

243
00:16:51,560 --> 00:16:53,360
When I was little, I caught a cricket.

244
00:16:54,960 --> 00:16:56,080
It was during the Dragon Boat Festival.

245
00:16:56,720 --> 00:16:59,320
It was right in the grass
in the backyard of my house.

246
00:17:00,280 --> 00:17:01,560
The little creature

247
00:17:02,640 --> 00:17:03,800
kept chirping.

248
00:17:05,120 --> 00:17:06,160
It seemed

249
00:17:07,280 --> 00:17:08,760
it had endless energy.

250
00:17:11,200 --> 00:17:12,120
It was very pleasant to hear.

251
00:17:14,400 --> 00:17:15,480
It seemed the chirping

252
00:17:16,560 --> 00:17:18,240
would never stop.

253
00:17:20,680 --> 00:17:22,360
But just after the seventh month
of the year,

254
00:17:25,280 --> 00:17:26,520
it died.

255
00:17:30,000 --> 00:17:31,520
I cried very hard.

256
00:17:34,080 --> 00:17:35,600
Later on, every year,

257
00:17:37,520 --> 00:17:39,840
I would catch a cricket.

258
00:17:41,320 --> 00:17:42,560
It was as if

259
00:17:43,960 --> 00:17:45,320
they made a deal.

260
00:17:46,160 --> 00:17:47,640
As soon as summer was over,

261
00:17:49,800 --> 00:17:51,160
all of them were dead.

262
00:17:54,080 --> 00:17:55,200
I can't remember

263
00:17:56,560 --> 00:17:58,160
what year

264
00:18:00,560 --> 00:18:02,200
I haven't cried since.

265
00:18:05,000 --> 00:18:06,000
Later on,

266
00:18:10,640 --> 00:18:12,840
no matter what kind of creature died,

267
00:18:17,040 --> 00:18:19,240
I never shed

268
00:18:21,600 --> 00:18:23,280
a single drop of tear.

269
00:18:42,720 --> 00:18:46,320
I can't save anyone!

270
00:18:48,840 --> 00:18:50,480
I can't save anyone.

271
00:19:15,440 --> 00:19:16,800
Magistrate, you are awake.

272
00:19:17,760 --> 00:19:19,360
Miss Cao prepared tea for you

273
00:19:19,440 --> 00:19:20,680
as well as water from the well.

274
00:19:22,080 --> 00:19:22,600
She...

275
00:19:23,200 --> 00:19:24,200
She is gone.

276
00:19:24,200 --> 00:19:25,760
She asked me to take good care of you.

277
00:19:30,000 --> 00:19:31,360
She asked me to tell you

278
00:19:31,440 --> 00:19:33,080
to go back after having tea.

279
00:19:33,240 --> 00:19:34,760
She will come back quite late.

280
00:20:11,780 --> 00:20:14,420
[Penglai County Magistrate's Office]

281
00:20:25,760 --> 00:20:26,400
Magistrate,

282
00:20:26,520 --> 00:20:27,840
The Esteemed Head has found out

283
00:20:27,840 --> 00:20:29,400
where the four soldiers went
that night.

284
00:20:29,520 --> 00:20:30,600
How could it be this tavern?

285
00:20:31,360 --> 00:20:33,640
This is the tavern

286
00:20:33,680 --> 00:20:34,600
where some people caused
a disturbance that night.

287
00:20:37,400 --> 00:20:37,920
This...

288
00:20:38,200 --> 00:20:39,200
Can you still recognize us?

289
00:20:39,320 --> 00:20:41,280
Gentlemen, it was a misunderstanding

290
00:20:41,840 --> 00:20:42,920
last time.

